 rq pf pg gg rr pi pj gj rs pl pm gm rt po pp pq rm rn ro bh" data-selectab=
le-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"pa il">10%</strong> is based on the numb=
er of weeks it survived on the bestseller list.</li></ul><p id=3D"6c73" cla=
